%--------- Variables  &  Procedures -------

/inch { 72 mul } def 
/TM 11 inch def
/BM -0.5 inch def
/LM 0 def
/RM 8.5 inch def
/str2print (abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz) def 

/fillpage
% parameter: stack:sring	
% function:	字符串填满当前页面:换行? 打印完?
{ 
	/str exch def
	{
		{ pop pop newline?  } str kshow
		reachButtom? { exit }if
	}loop
} def 

/newline? 
% function:	判断是否换行 
{
	currentpoint pop RM gt
	{newline} if
}def

/newline
% function:	换行
{ 
	currentpoint 5 sub
	exch pop
	LM exch moveto 
} def 

/reachButtom?
% parameter:	
% function:	到页面底部?
{ 
	currentpoint exch pop%get x-axis
	BM lt
} def 

